==爭議==
[[File:Treinamento3.jpg|300px]]
2005年[[紐約大學法學院|紐約大學法學院]]的一份報告指出，特別警察行動營涉嫌非法槍殺4名青少年，後者據稱是拒捕的販毒者。報告指出是特別警察行動營成員篡改了錄像以證明受害者有罪，但實際上並未從4人身上發現任何武器，他們也都沒有前科。<ref>[http://www.extrajudicialexecutions.org/application/media/E_CN_4_2005_7_Add_1%202005.pdf Report on extra judicial executions] {{Wayback|url=http://www.extrajudicialexecutions.org/application/media/E_CN_4_2005_7_Add_1%202005.pdf |date=20210121073449 }} of the New York University School of Law: "BOPE officers falsified the crime scene to incriminate the victims in an attempt to make them seem like members of a drug trafficking gang. No weapons were found with the victims and none of them had a history of criminal activity."</ref>

[[國際特赦組織|國際特赦組織]]指出巴西軍方及警方慣於採用暴力的、鎮壓式的手段執法，這危害到了許多人的正當權益。該組織特別指出了特別警察行動營濫殺平民之舉。<ref>''[http://www.amnesty.org/en/library/info/AMR19/025/2005/en «They come shooting…»] {{Wayback|url=http://www.amnesty.org/en/library/info/AMR19/025/2005/en |date=20140805125928 }}. Amnesty International, The maintenance of order at the heart of socially excluded populations'', report of 2005.</ref>

